728025f-b.text:
Springfield Boulevard, near the S.E. corner of 116th Avenue, showing an old Hendrickson homestead. There were several Hendrickson farmhouses in the village of Springfield. The property was owned by H. Kromenacher in 1891 and by Florence C. Smith in 1918.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  1925

2-3) The same, at a later date.

P.L.Sperr  March 9, 1927
